text: Yahuud Quzeyri Yallih baxa itteeh, Nasaara Masiic (Nabii Qiisa kinnuk) Yallih baxa itte, toh ken maxcoy ken afat taniy usun diraabah ginnaasiteeni, usun woo maxcot keenik duma koroosite marih maxco gabbaaqoonuh ken edde ceelan, Yalli ken qiday isi racmatak ken yayxaarayik mannaay cakkik deedal fanah elle makkootaanam
